{"tid":1444558,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"受阿澤盤問對比雨傘同現在 阿詩有意參選立法會","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:36:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ffedef937078c5a37d62a788959283f558358a9","tid":1444558,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:46:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190811/20746779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190811%2F20746779&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqnO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=17d73261\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190811%2F20746779&h=de5c754c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190811/20746779</a><br />\n<br />\n受阿澤盤問對比雨傘同現在<br />\n阿詩有意參選立法會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190811/large/1565439607_32a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190811%2Flarge%2F1565439607_32a5.jpg&h=64b85630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿詩接受阿澤盤問，直言抗爭底線是不傷害無辜的人。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩接受杜汶澤網台新節目「CEO盤問室」盤問，前晚播出首集，二人在節目中大談最近的反送中事件。阿澤甫開始問阿詩在聯合國人權理事會中發表演說，被中國代表阻撓發言，她直言因為場地太空曠，所以當刻完全聽不到對方說甚麼，而且更以昆蟲來形容對方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190811/large/1565439606_d499.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190811%2Flarge%2F1565439606_d499.jpg&h=7b90c174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿詩表示在聯合國人權理事會發言被打斷，其實聽不到對方在說甚麼。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n挺身擋子彈<br />\n<br />\n阿澤問到阿詩是否有意參選做立法會議員，她表示有思考過，若真的進入立法會後不能做些正經的事，她說：「如果真係要做，其實係要曳啲！」阿澤聞言即提議阿詩加入民建聯，阿詩即時爆笑。問到2014年雨傘運動，她有份成立糾察隊，叫大家不要衝擊被指是「左膠」，她澄清沒有成立糾察隊：「因為嗰陣時話要出橡膠子彈，大家就好擔心，我哋成立一個文化監暴，萬一出橡膠子彈，我哋企喺警察前面，希望佢哋認得我同明仔（黃耀明），做個緩衝角色。」對於現時局勢，阿詩認為絕不容許：「你冇諗過警隊係可以癲到咁樣㗎嘛，根本係用警隊嚟去打死你班人咁樣，唔會用番五年前想法去對𠵱家呢個政府。」<br />\n<br />\n對於抗爭的底線，阿詩表示絕不傷害無辜的人，她說：「仇恨嗰樣嘢係咪可以去幫到件事呢？面對一個咁嘅極權，有邊啲窿窿罅罅可以去做，7.1係一條罅，入咗去嗰個位令佢哋冇辦法唔面對，我唔覺得係一個暴力，只不過係打爛咗啲玻璃，但過程入面大家冇去傷害到任何人，呢個係好緊要。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：唐如  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【姐匙Talk】精叻擦鞋怨香港人阻搵食<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n余香凝減肥寧縮胸"},{"pid":"b91808187607268c3da7b6ca5037999590e8f118","tid":1444558,"uid":176114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:34:05.000Z","msg":"個標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話有考慮過，但冇意參選喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3883b9c74551a05cc48d043c605b36575d9b00","tid":1444558,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b91808187607268c3da7b6ca5037999590e8f118","tid":1444558,"uid":176114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:34:05.000Z","msg":"個標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話有考慮過，但冇意參選喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:36:21.000Z","msg":"毒果咁樣擺 hocc 上枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}